Okay, well, um, what about this?

367
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,320
什么意思
What does this mean?

368
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:13,870
酗酒  乱刷卡和熬夜看电视 都没啥好处
Wine, credit card and late night television are a bad combination.

369
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,530
好吧
All right, fine.

370
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:18,470
那个长长的拥抱呢
What about that really long hug?

371
