393
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:27,370
你在搞什么玩意
What are you working on?

394
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:29,420
弩弓
Crossbow.

395
00:19:31,390 --> 00:19:33,620
伙计们  我能说几句吗
Hey, guys, can I just say something?

396
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:35,130
